- Use inline mapping when returning DTOs from loaders/actions.
- The DTO should only contain the minimal number of fields that are needed by the UI components.
- Let TypeScript infer the types without explicit type annotations

Example:

```typescript
// Correct approach - direct inline mapping
return {
  todos: todoEntities.map(todo => ({
    id: todo.id,
    title: todo.title,
    completed: todo.completed
  }))
}

// Avoid this - no separate mappers or DTO types
function mapToDTO(entity) { ... }  // Don't do this

// Avoid this - no explicit DTO type definitions
type TodoDTO = { ... }  // Don't do this
```
